Package: intradayModel
Title: State-Space Modeling of Intraday Trading Volume
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2023-4-11
Description: Maximum-likelihood parameter estimation for state-space models fit to time-series data.  
            Fitting is primarily via the Expectation-Maximization (EM) algorithm. Functions for 
            prediction and filtering are also provided. The package is based on the papers: Chen, Feng, and Palomar (2016).
